Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.63,0:00:09.47,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,When he called out to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.47,0:00:11.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I had something of a premonition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.19,0:00:13.55,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What sort of premonition?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.99,0:00:25.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,That perhaps I would... fall in love with this person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.87,0:00:28.79,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What's he like?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.27,0:00:42.59,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,His name is Natori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.75,0:00:56.75,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Simple relations
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.15,0:01:28.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well, hello there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.99,0:01:35.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Even if you ask me "why"... It just\Nseemed like you were free.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:39.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Did I really look like I had a bunch of free time?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.99,0:01:46.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Say, have you been rather bored lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:49.43,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Why did you come with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.43,0:01:51.15,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.99,0:01:53.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,So, where do you want to go from here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.99,0:01:56.87,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Anywhere is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.87,0:02:00.95,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go and have some\Nfun at an amusement park?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.99,0:02:18.79,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,So this is an "amusement park"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:58.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Wait, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.71,0:03:01.07,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:02.95,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Is this your first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:14.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Natori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:24.27,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.99,0:03:29.47,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.27,0:03:38.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Natori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:53.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What are you doing right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.99,0:03:56.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You're the only thing I think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.51,0:04:01.43,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Keiko: Did you stay in touch with him after that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.27,0:04:08.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Nozomi-chan, I made some tea for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:12.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Thanks, mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:17.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You made Earl Grey today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.99,0:04:19.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah, doesn't it smell good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:22.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Don't stay up too late now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.43,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:41.27,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hey, Natori!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:44.59,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Shoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:49.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You're drooling.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.71,0:04:54.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You got yourself a new girlfriend,\Ndidn't you, Natori?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:57.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What's with all the questions? Did\Nyou get yourself a boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.99,0:04:59.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well, perhaps I will soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.99,0:05:04.67,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well then, same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.99,0:05:10.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Which means you {\i1}do{\i0} have a girlfriend! You\Njerk, getting all happy all by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.99,0:05:14.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid! I never said I had a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:18.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Geez, you're the one who dumped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.99,0:05:21.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You're the one who went and\Ngot ahead of himself, Natori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.99,0:05:25.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well, looking back on it, it was rather entertaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:28.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:31.71,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The "Anything Goes" Favorite Circle
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.99,0:05:36.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:40.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I saw everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.99,0:05:43.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You're still hanging out with Shoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:48.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and? Oh, because I was\Nwith her just a second ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:50.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Are you guys retarded?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:56.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You were so depressed just a month ago, going\Non and on about how Shoko dumped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.63,0:06:00.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It was the same old same old for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.99,0:06:04.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Don't go on babbling about petty things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:10.47,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I've completely cut ties with Shoko!\NI'm dating a younger girl now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.15,0:06:15.59,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What, compensated dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.99,0:06:17.71,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm going to kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.27,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Introduce her to us next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.99,0:06:22.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Have her bring along some friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.99,0:06:24.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Come on, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.99,0:06:28.87,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'll get around to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.15,0:06:36.43,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Would you like to see my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.27,0:06:42.03,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I haven't really been in someone else's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.15,0:06:45.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Because you're used to hotel rooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Na-Natori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Do you have any idea why I invited you over?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.99,0:06:56.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,As you can see, I live with my parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:06:59.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But they're both out tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.99,0:07:03.35,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I wanted to do it in a different setting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.99,0:07:06.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.99,0:07:09.59,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I know you want it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:19.95,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Geez, who could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.71,0:07:23.71,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yes, Natori speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.43,0:07:27.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Huh?! You're already on your way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.43,0:07:29.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:30.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:34.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,My parents did what they needed to do,\Nand said they're on their way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:36.71,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well then, I should be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:40.71,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.87,0:07:45.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Huh? This is the last bus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:49.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,We've got an hour before the next one\Ncomes. Man, I hate the countryside!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:51.31,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.31,0:07:53.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:57.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I always ride my bike to the train station.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:59.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I don't really ride the bus that often.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.99,0:08:03.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll just have to wait it out, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:07.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The moon is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.99,0:08:10.59,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,And the night air is nice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.99,0:08:15.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to make you feel even better?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.87,0:08:22.59,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Natori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:26.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Your reaction is always over the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.95,0:08:34.87,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I like that about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.87,0:08:39.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,People might show up in a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.99,0:08:43.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's go somewhere we can't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:49.27,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,We can't take our time at my house since my\Nparents will be home any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:50.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.99,0:08:54.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Don't worry! No one will come\Nthrough here at this hour
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.99,0:08:59.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I know you want it. I can see it in your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.99,0:09:42.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I wonder what that look was about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:51.66,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Western Style Bar
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:53.15,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.27,0:09:57.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,She's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.99,0:10:00.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Did she bring any friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:02.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Next time, next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.99,0:10:06.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,This is Nozomi-chan. Be nice to her, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:09.71,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hey, can you drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:14.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,She's fine! She'll have a beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:18.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,They look like they get along well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.99,0:10:28.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.99,0:10:34.15,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I only see her nights during the\Nweek ever since I met her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.15,0:10:36.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Only at night? Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:42.15,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,She said he's busy during the day with\Nclub activities. He said he has practice\Non Sundays as well. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.39,0:10:47.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah! As expected of a top student!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.99,0:10:48.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You sure are straight-laced.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.99,0:10:51.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly! Whoever said I was straight-laced?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.99,0:10:54.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Meeting up at night could only mean one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.99,0:10:57.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well, you do do {\i1}that{\i0} at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:02.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Oh, {\i1}that{\i0}? Ah, I don't really\Nsee it happening, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.99,0:11:04.91,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I sure am jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.91,0:11:08.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,She sure likes it. Nozomi is generally into {\i1}that{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.99,0:11:09.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,U-Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.99,0:11:12.91,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What was that? I can't hear you all very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:14.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Come on, now! The poor thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.99,0:11:18.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? Are you feeling ill?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:22.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Oh, I got it! You want to go to a hotel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:26.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:33.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:35.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Thanks for the drink!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.99,0:11:37.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Geez, okay, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.99,0:11:39.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What, you're not buying one, Natori?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:43.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:45.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,A little birdie told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:49.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,That your current girlfriend is rather young.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:55.35,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Damn it! I told those jerks not\Nto talk to you about it, Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.51,0:11:59.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What are you going on about? What, are you\Ntrying to be considerate of my feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:01.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Not in the slightest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.51,0:12:05.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I heard she's pretty cute. Not bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.59,0:12:08.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:12.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I feel rather bad for her that she\Nhas to date a sadist like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:14.47,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Who are you calling a sadist?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.47,0:12:18.39,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You're having sex with her, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.11,0:12:22.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You know, like playing Molester, or telling her\Nto come out without any underwear on.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.99,0:12:24.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You made me cry quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.99,0:12:26.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You know you liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:29.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What sort of girl is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:30.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Let me meet her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.99,0:12:32.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Not gonna happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.99,0:12:34.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,She's not at home during the day\Nbecause of club activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.27,0:12:38.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Besides, I haven't called her on the phone yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:44.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Oh? Then that's all the more reason to call her!\NShe'll be happy to get the first call from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.99,0:12:56.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's making a weird sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:18.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,See? She's not home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yes? Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.99,0:13:23.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you {\i1}are{\i0} home! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:25.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Natori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:29.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Come on out here! There's someone\Nwho insists on meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.99,0:13:36.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Um... I-I can't right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.99,0:13:40.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,My mom isn't home at the moment and\Nshe asked me to watch the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.99,0:13:42.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine if you lock the door on the way out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.99,0:13:44.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:48.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Come on! Let's meet up during\Nthe day once in a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:54.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,She said she'll come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.99,0:13:56.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.87,0:14:18.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Nozomi,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.99,0:14:22.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,this is the girl who insisted on meeting\Nyou. Her name is Shoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:25.03,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.95,0:14:29.87,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,This is rather unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:33.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I can't believe you'd date someone like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:34.79,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:39.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,At the very least, she isn't the type\Nyou've dated up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.19,0:14:42.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Shut it! Are you happy now\Nthat you've seen Nozomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:44.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What, you're shooing me away already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:49.63,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,That's not how it is! This is the first time\Nwe've met up during the day. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:54.47,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well, let's get going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:01.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You're thinking of something weird, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.99,0:15:03.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You're the one thinking of something, not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.99,0:15:07.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Nozomi-chan, is Natori mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.99,0:15:09.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Let me know if he is! I'll kick his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:12.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:16.83,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Shoko! Butt out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.55,0:15:19.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hey, Nozomi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:22.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Do you want to go see a movie together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.19,0:15:25.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,There's one that I want to see,\Nbut it's boring to go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.19,0:15:27.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Which movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:31.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well, Brad Pitt's new movie came out last week!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.19,0:15:32.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Oh, nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.19,0:15:35.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,How about it, Nozomi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:39.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Umm, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.19,0:15:41.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:43.35,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hey! No-Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.35,0:15:47.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You jerk! Go after her!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:50.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Shoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.19,0:15:54.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You're apologizing to the wrong person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.19,0:16:02.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.19,0:16:04.27,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What's the matter? You're acting differently.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.19,0:16:08.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You've got a terrible fever!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.27,0:16:12.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'll be fine. I just want to take a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:14.95,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What are you going on about taking\Na break?! Not with a fever like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:17.43,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Wait here! I'll go and get someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.55,0:16:18.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.51,0:16:20.47,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.43,0:16:24.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hold me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:44.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Natori-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:00.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Natori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:09.63,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Let's do it like we usually do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.87,0:17:12.15,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Nozomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:32.43,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It feels so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.99,0:17:38.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Can you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.99,0:17:41.59,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,How embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.99,0:17:53.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Now it's my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.99,0:18:08.95,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Natori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.95,0:18:10.59,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Do you want it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.71,0:18:28.55,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Natori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:37.27,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Natori-san! Does it feel good for you, Natori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.99,0:18:39.43,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.59,0:18:41.55,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Good. I'm happy to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.55,0:18:43.15,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,How about you, Nozomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:46.71,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It feels really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:28.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Natori-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:32.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Thank you for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.99,0:19:34.95,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.95,0:19:37.87,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I love you, Natori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.99,0:19:42.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.59,0:19:51.79,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hey! Why are you crying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.87,0:19:55.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Come on, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:58.71,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I'll pick on you some more once you cheer up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:12.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,When are you going to introduce\Nus to Nozorru-chan's friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:16.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well, the thing is, she's been flaking\Nout on me ever since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:19.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I've tried to call her several times,\Nbut I can't get ahold of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:23.47,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,There's always a weird sound,\Nand she never picks up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:25.91,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,She dumped you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.75,0:20:31.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.51,0:20:33.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Geez, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.51,0:20:35.43,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,So you were the one on the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:43.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It was just a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:46.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But I just happened to be in Nozomi's room,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.99,0:20:49.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,so I was able to receive your phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.99,0:20:52.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You said something about a computer\Nconnection, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.99,0:20:57.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,That phone number was a personal\Nline she used for chat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.99,0:20:59.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Where's Nozomi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.99,0:21:04.11,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,You didn't say anything on the\Nphone, but what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.11,0:21:08.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Well, Nozomi died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:10.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,She died about 10 days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.99,0:21:14.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Nozomi was sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.99,0:21:18.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I didn't know anything about it until it was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:20.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,What sickness did she have?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.99,0:21:24.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Her mom wouldn't give me\Nthe details of the sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:28.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But it appears she couldn't sweat\Nif she went out into the sunlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:33.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I stopped by her house today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.99,0:21:37.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,And you see, Natori-san, the\Nreason I had to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.99,0:21:39.67,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,is because I wanted you to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:46.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Our chat logs have been all about\Nyou for the past two months.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:51.43,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It might be a bit of a burden, but I want\Nyou to know how Nozomi felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:56.83,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Nozomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.83,0:21:59.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,He might have been a little too\Npushy with me at times,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.99,0:22:04.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,but I think he's really kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:08.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,All of his college friends were kind people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.99,0:22:11.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I drank alcohol. It made me feel grown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.99,0:22:14.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Natori-san sure can hold his liquor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.99,0:22:18.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It made me think about how mature he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.99,0:22:21.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Natori-san's room was unexpectedly clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.99,0:22:26.87,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It made me really happy just to be surrounded\Nby all of the things he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.87,0:22:30.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,He said he loves me! I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.99,0:22:33.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It's really just by chance that we met!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.99,0:22:37.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But I really want to cherish this opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.99,0:22:41.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,And this is the final message.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.99,0:22:45.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,From the day before she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.99,0:22:51.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It may be that I have fallen\Nin love out of convenience.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.51,0:22:55.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,But I'm fine with that. I love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.51,0:22:58.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I really love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.51,0:23:02.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I just wish I could be with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:36.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}yosomi wo shitetara chansu ga nigeteiku
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:36.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Your chance will get way if you don't focus
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:42.07,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}mou matenai yo sasso aoutte READY GO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.63,0:23:42.07,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I can't wait anymore, come on, let's meet, Ready Go
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.55,0:23:50.63,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kotoba no uragawa mirai no yukue toka
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.55,0:23:50.63,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Rather than thinking about words\Nthat hold some meaning for the future
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.51,0:23:54.55,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}mendou na koto wo souzou suru yori
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.51,0:23:54.55,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,and other bothersome things,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.07,0:23:57.75,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}suki wa suki de ii ja nai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.07,0:23:57.75,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Just like whatever you want to like
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:24:04.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}hottokenai yo karada no oku ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.47,0:24:04.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I can let it go, and within me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.19,0:24:11.59,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ima kanjiteriru atsui kurasshu honoo ni natte
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.19,0:24:11.59,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The passionate crash I feel turns into flames
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.35,0:24:15.35,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}kokoro sae mo makikomu
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.35,0:24:15.35,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,and even my heart wasn't saved from it
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.59,0:24:20.47,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Get you! Get you! ii kagen na kimochi
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.59,0:24:20.47,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Get you! Get you! These half-hearted feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.99,0:24:23.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Get you! Get you! sonna mon' ja nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.99,0:24:23.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Get you! Get you! No, it's not really like that
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.99,0:24:30.75,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}yowaki ke tobaseba ato ni kawaru
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.99,0:24:30.75,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Kick those feelings of weakness\Nand change will come afterward
