Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.43,0:24:34.43,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hit me! Hit me! Those melancholic expressions
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.95,0:24:37.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hit me! Hit me! poosu nante shitete
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.95,0:24:37.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hit me! Hit me! Just get on with it and strike a pose
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.71,0:24:42.67,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}tsukamaeyou I can ready go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.71,0:24:42.67,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Let's get it all I can, Ready Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.83,0:24:54.91,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}hara hara shitenakya ikiteru ki ga shinai
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.83,0:24:54.91,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like living if there's no excitement
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.79,0:25:00.07,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}taikutsu yori mo suriru mezashite Ready go
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.79,0:25:00.07,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Thrills will always be better than\Nboring things, so Ready Go
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.79,0:25:08.87,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ashita no watashi wa kinou to nitenai
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.79,0:25:08.87,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I am different from the person I was yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.75,0:25:12.79,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}mainichi umare kawareru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.75,0:25:12.79,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,And if I'm always reborn everyday like this
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.43,0:25:16.07,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}mamoru mono wa nai ja nai
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.43,0:25:16.07,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I have nothing more to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.59,0:25:22.75,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}minogasanai yo karada no oku ni
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.59,0:25:22.75,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I can let it pass, and within me,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.47,0:25:29.67,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ima todoiteiru kimi no biito ookiku natte
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.47,0:25:29.67,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,The beats from you become bigger
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.51,0:25:33.63,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}tsuyoku mune wo ugokasu
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.51,0:25:33.63,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Invigorating my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.79,0:25:38.71,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Get you! Get you! chotto hazushite mo
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.79,0:25:38.71,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Get you! Get you! Even if I let it off a bit
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.31,0:25:42.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Get you! Get you! doutte koto nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.31,0:25:42.19,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Get you! Get you! It won't affect me at all
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.19,0:25:48.75,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}naritai jibun ni watashi nareru
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.19,0:25:48.75,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I can become whatever I want
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.51,0:25:52.71,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hit me! Hit me! ai toka yume ni wa
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.51,0:25:52.71,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hit me! Hit me! In love and dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.23,0:25:56.07,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hit me! Hit me! ruuru nanka nai yo
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.23,0:25:56.07,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hit me! Hit me! There are no rules
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.87,0:26:01.03,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}dakishimeyou I can ready go!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.87,0:26:01.03,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Let's all embrace it I can, Ready Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.83,0:26:26.79,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}isogu kimochi wo osaetakunai ima sugu
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.83,0:26:26.79,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I don't want to hold back from the rush, it's now or never
