Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.39,0:26:34.35,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Get you! Get you! No it's not really like that
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.35,0:26:40.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}yowaki ke tobaseba go ni kawaru
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.35,0:26:40.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Kick those feelings of weakness\Nand change will come afterward
