Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.83,0:26:44.79,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hit me! Hit me! Those melancholic expressions
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.31,0:26:48.31,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hit me! Hit me! poosu nante shitete
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.31,0:26:48.31,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Hit me! Hit me! Just get on with it and strike a pose
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.99,0:26:54.83,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,{\an8}tsukamaeyou I can ready go!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.99,0:26:54.83,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,Let's get it all, I can Ready Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.51,0:27:32.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,When I told Nozomi loved her
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.51,0:27:36.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,that really was the first time I said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.51,0:27:41.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I said it from the heart, but it might have been\Ndue to the state I was in at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.99,0:27:44.51,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,It was so easy to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.51,0:27:47.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,but it wasn't the same for Nozomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.99,0:27:52.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking this whole time about\Nwhen Nozomi came out that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.99,0:27:56.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I know why she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.99,0:28:00.99,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,She wanted to see you, Natori.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.99,0:28:03.59,Hardsub,,0,0,0,,I could see it in her eyes.